      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Marcin Szubert</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:139px;\"><a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=5Zl30U0AAAAJ&amp;hl=en\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/1/1b/MarcinSzubert.jpg\" width=\"137\" height=\"150\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:MarcinSzubert.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Marcin Szubert <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Marcin Grzegorz Szubert</b>,<br />\na Polish computer scientist and postdoc at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Vermont\">University of Vermont</a>, previously assistant professor at the Institute of Computing Science, \n<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pozna%C5%84_University_of_Technology\">Poznań University of Technology</a>, where he defended his Ph.D. thesis in 2014 on the concept of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shaping_%28psychology%29\">shaping</a> in <a href=\"/Reinforcement_Learning\" title=\"Reinforcement Learning\">reinforcement learning</a> experimentally verified in nontrivial sequential decision making domains, \nincluding the board games of <a href=\"/Othello\" title=\"Othello\">Othello</a> and small board <a href=\"/Go\" title=\"Go\">Go</a> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nHis further research interests include <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">computational intelligence</a>, <a href=\"/Genetic_Programming#EvolutionaryComputation\" title=\"Genetic Programming\">evolutionary computation</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coevolution#Algorithms\">coevolutionary algorithms</a> and the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2048_%28video_game%29\">puzzle game 2048</a> \n<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2009\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2009</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcin_Szubert&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2009\">2009</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcin_Szubert&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2009\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a>, <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>Coevolutionary Temporal Difference Learning for Othello</i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#CIG\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Symposium on Computational Intelligence and Games</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/wjaskowski/pub/papers/szubert09coevolutionary.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>Coevolutionary Reinforcement Learning and its Application to Othello</i>. M.Sc. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pozna%C5%84_University_of_Technology\">Poznań University of Technology</a>, supervisor <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://mszubert.github.io/papers/Szubert_2009_MSC.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcin_Szubert&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/5586054?arnumber=5586054\">Coevolutionary Temporal Difference Learning for small-board Go</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#EC\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Congress on Evolutionary Computation</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i>Learning N-Tuple Networks for Othello by Coevolutionary Gradient Search</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/gecco/gecco2011.html\">GECCO 2011</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/mszubert/pub/krawiec2011gecco.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a>, <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://content.sciendo.com/view/journals/amcs/21/4/article-p717.xml\">Evolving small-board Go players using Coevolutionary Temporal Difference Learning with Archives</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Journal_of_Applied_Mathematics_and_Computer_Science\">International Journal of Applied Mathematics and Computer Science</a>, Vol. 21, No. 4&#160;» <a href=\"/Go\" title=\"Go\">Go</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a>, <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i>Learning Board Evaluation Function for Othello by Hybridizing Coevolution with Temporal Difference Learning</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://control.ibspan.waw.pl:3000/mainpage\">Control and Cybernetics</a>, Vol. 40, No. 3, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/wjaskowski/pub/papers/szubert2011learning.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a>  (<b>2012</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-642-32964-7_22\">Autonomous Shaping via Coevolutionary Selection of Training Experience</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/ppsn/ppsn2012-2.html\">12. PPSN</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a>, <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.academia.edu/4601823/On_Scalability_Generalization_and_Hybridization_of_Coevolutionary_Learning_A_Case_Study_for_Othello\">On Scalability, Generalization, and Hybridization of Coevolutionary Learning: a Case Study for Othello</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TOCIAIGAMES\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Computational Intelligence and AI in Games</a>, Vol. 5, No. 3</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a>, <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a href=\"/Pawe%C5%82_Liskowski\" title=\"Paweł Liskowski\">Paweł Liskowski</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>Shaping Fitness Function for Evolutionary Learning of Game Strategies</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/gecco/gecco2013.html\">GECCO 2013</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/wjaskowski/pub/papers/szubert2013shaping.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a href=\"/Pawe%C5%82_Liskowski\" title=\"Paweł Liskowski\">Paweł Liskowski</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>Improving Coevolution by Random Sampling</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/gecco/gecco2013.html\">GECCO 2013</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/mszubert/pub/jaskowski2013gecco.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a>, <a href=\"/Pawe%C5%82_Liskowski\" title=\"Paweł Liskowski\">Paweł Liskowski</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>Multi-Criteria Comparison of Coevolution and Temporal Difference Learning on Othello</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/evoW/evoappl2014.html\">EvoApplications 2014</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.springer.com/gp/book/9783662455227\">Applications of Evolutionary Computation</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a>, <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/mszubert/projects/2048.html\">Temporal Difference Learning of N-Tuple Networks for the Game 2048</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#CIG\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Conference on Computational Intelligence and Games</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/mszubert/pub/szubert2014cig.pdf\">pdf</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>Coevolutionary Shaping for Reinforcement Learning</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pozna%C5%84_University_of_Technology\">Poznań University of Technology</a>, supervisor <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a>, co-supervisor <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/mszubert/pub/phdthesis.pdf\">pdf</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://mszubert.github.io/papers/Szubert_2014_PHD.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcin_Szubert&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a>, <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a href=\"/Pawe%C5%82_Liskowski\" title=\"Paweł Liskowski\">Paweł Liskowski</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a> (<b>2015</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-319-16549-3_32\">The Role of Behavioral Diversity and Difficulty of Opponents in Coevolving Game-Playing Agents</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/evoW/evoappl2015.html\">EvoApplications 2015</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a> (<b>2016</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/7180338\">Coevolutionary CMA-ES for Knowledge-Free Learning of Game Position Evaluation</a></i>. <a href=\"/IEEE#TOCIAIGAMES\" title=\"IEEE\">IEEE Transactions on Computational Intelligence and AI in Games</a>, Vol. 8, No. 4 <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a href=\"/Pawe%C5%82_Liskowski\" title=\"Paweł Liskowski\">Paweł Liskowski</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a>, <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a> (<b>2016</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://content.sciendo.com/view/journals/amcs/26/1/article-p215.xml\">The performance profile: A multi–criteria performance evaluation method for test–based problems</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/International_Journal_of_Applied_Mathematics_and_Computer_Science\">International Journal of Applied Mathematics and Computer Science</a>, Vol. 26, No. 1</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcin_Szubert&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://mszubert.github.io/\">Marcin Szubert</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/mszubert/\">Marcin Szubert - Home Page</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/mszubert/projects/2048.html\">Temporal Difference Learning of N-Tuple Networks for the Game 2048</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=5Zl30U0AAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Marcin Szubert - Google Scholar Citations</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/mszubert\">Marcin Szubert · GitHub</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marcin_Szubert&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=5Zl30U0AAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Marcin Szubert - Google Scholar Citations</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>Coevolutionary Shaping for Reinforcement Learning</i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pozna%C5%84_University_of_Technology\">Poznań University of Technology</a>, supervisor <a href=\"/Krzysztof_Krawiec\" title=\"Krzysztof Krawiec\">Krzysztof Krawiec</a>, co-supervisor <a href=\"/Wojciech_Ja%C5%9Bkowski\" title=\"Wojciech Jaśkowski\">Wojciech Jaśkowski</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/mszubert/pub/phdthesis.pdf\">pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.put.poznan.pl/mszubert/projects/2048.html\">Temporal Difference Learning of N-Tuple Networks for the Game 2048</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marcin Szubert</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/s/Szubert:Marcin_Grzegorz.html\">dblp: Marcin Grzegorz Szubert</a></span>\n</li>\